Class TkHTML

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.takes.tk.TkWrap

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Take

    public final class TkHTML
extends TkWrap
    HTML take.

    This take returns an HTML response by wrapping the provided content into RsHTML.

    The class is immutable and thread-safe.

    0.1
